Documentation for Global Arrays
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- user.pdf -- User's Manual for GA 3.0 in Adobe PDF format. 
- Supercomputing94.pdf -- The original SC'94 paper describing GA.

You need to use Acrobat Reader version at least 3.0 to view and print these
documents. This program is available for free from:

    http://www.adobe.com/prodindex/acrobat/readstep.html

More documentation is available at the GA homepage:

    http://www.emsl.pnl.gov/docs/global
